      "comment": "LAVENDER LANE (8) has been in the money at the last couple here when racing on speed, last outing finishing third beaten 5 lengths (20.29). Good beginner but will need a little luck early crossing from an outside draw. Sure to be about the mark. ERROR CODE (2) settled close to the lead but checked in the run and turned spotting a start, missing the frame when fourth (20.55) at this track over 342m in a Grade 6. Should be in this for a long way. RATBAG RUBY (4) latest effort finished 4th over 342m at this track beaten 6 lengths (20.42) behind Zipping Kentucky in a Maiden on June 22. Can hit the frame with the right run. IDEALISTIC (6) is a newcomer from the Tiarn Jaensch kennel. Respect any moves in the market.",
